snippet.textDisplay: I am here after listening to Khalasi and Coke studio Pakistan Kana yaari. They integrated the song and the rap so well as in they felt like one whole music to the ears. The big problem with this song is its rap For eg take a loot at Khalasi the whole song is Gujarati the rap even its accent is so Gujarati and yet meaningful. But in this song we are mixing some English words like hardcore parkour the whole essence of the song is lost due to that rap. There are some good rappers out there who can make some good Hindi or pure Hindi raps. Coke studio please don't go for Big Rappers just so you get some views invest in some good rappers to produce good songs.
